    TeleplanResponse
    TeleplanAPI.getLogList()
    Procedure parameters: None Parameters to TeleplanBroker are ExternalAction = "AgetLogList" Results from TeleplanBroker are: "SUCCESS" "FAILURE" This will return a file contain a list (1 logname/line) of logs the user can download The format of the logname is: 001E2805.LOG To convert this to the same style as the www download name you must extract the century from the first character (0..Z 0=20, Z=56) extract the Month which is the 4th character (A (Jan)..L(Dec)) Then you would create the filename CCYY_MM_DD_Gdd.LOG The filename 001E2805.LOG would convert to 2001_5_28_G05.LOG
